<eesti>Paragrahvi 2: </eesti>
<inglise>Section 2: </inglise>
<eesti>1) m&otilde;iste "arvestuslik &otilde;ppekoha maksumus" muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>1) the definition of "calculated cost of a student place" is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&otilde;ppekoha arvestuslik maksumus - konkreetse &otilde;ppekoha arvestuslik hind, mis moodustub igal aastal riigieelarve alusel arvutatud &otilde;ppekoha baasmaksumuse ning &otilde;ppekavale ja &otilde;ppevormile kinnitatud koefitsientide korrutisena; &ldquo;; </eesti>
<inglise>"calculated cost of a student place" means the calculated price of a specific student place formed from the basic cost of a student place which is calculated annually on the basis of state budget and multiplied by the factors approved for the curriculum and form of study; &ldquo;; </inglise>
<eesti>2) t&auml;iendatakse p&auml;rast m&otilde;istet "&otilde;ppekoha arvestuslik maksumus" m&otilde;istetega "&otilde;ppekoha baasmaksumus" ja "&otilde;ppekulud" j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>2) is amended by adding the definitions of "basic cost of a student place" and "study costs" after the definition of "calculated cost of a student place" worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&otilde;ppekoha baasmaksumus - igal aastal Vabariigi Valitsuse kinnitatud &otilde;ppekoha minimaalmaksumus, mis sisaldab &uuml;he &uuml;li&otilde;pilase &otilde;petamiseks tehtavaid kulutusi, v&auml;lja arvatud kulutused investeeringutele; </eesti>
<inglise>"basic cost of a student place" means the minimum cost of a student place which is approved annually by the Government of the Republic and which comprises the expenses incurred for the education of one student, except expenses for investments; </inglise>
<eesti>&otilde;ppekulud - konkreetsel &otilde;ppeaastal &uuml;likooli poolt &uuml;he &otilde;ppekoha finantseerimiseks tehtavad kulutused; &ldquo;. </eesti>
<inglise>"study costs" means the expenses incurred by the university in order to finance a student place during a given academic year; &ldquo;. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
