<eesti>"&sect; 13 (1). </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 13 (1). </inglise>
<eesti>Riiklik koolitustellimus </eesti>
<inglise>State commissioned education </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Riikliku koolitustellimuse esitab &uuml;likoolile Haridusministeerium, l&auml;htudes prognoositavast k&otilde;rgharidusega spetsialistide vajadusest t&ouml;&ouml;turul, ministeeriumide, omavalitsus&uuml;ksuste liitude, registreeritud kutse- ja ametiliitude (&uuml;hingute) ning &uuml;likoolide ettepanekutest, samuti riiklikuks koolitustellimuseks riigieelarves etten&auml;htud vahenditest. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The provision of state commissioned education in a university shall be determined by the Ministry of Education based on the foreseeable need for specialists with higher education in the labour market, on the proposals of ministries, local government associations, registered professional and occupational associations (unions) and universities, and on the funds designated for state commissioned education in the state budget. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Riiklik koolitustellimus vormistatakse &uuml;likooli ja Haridusministeeriumi vahelise lepinguna ning see sisaldab: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The provision of state commissioned education shall be formalised as a contract between a university and the Ministry of Education and the contract shall include: </inglise>
<eesti>1) riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatavate &otilde;ppekohtade arvu vastavalt &otilde;ppekavadele ja &otilde;ppevormidele; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the number of student places formed on the basis of state commissioned education pursuant to the curricula and forms of study; </inglise>
<eesti>2) riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekoha baasmaksumust; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the basic cost of a student place formed on the basis of state commissioned education; </inglise>
<eesti>3) riikliku koolitustellimuse t&auml;itmiseks &uuml;likoolile riigieelarvest raha eraldamise korda; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the procedure for allocation of funds from the state budget to the university for the provision of state commissioned education; </inglise>
<eesti>4) &uuml;likooli poolt Haridusministeeriumile riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohtadel &otilde;ppivate &uuml;li&otilde;pilaste arvestuse pidamiseks vajalike andmete esitamise korda ja t&auml;htaegu; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the procedure and terms for submission of information by the university to the Ministry of Education, in order to keep record of students who study in student places formed on the basis of state commissioned education; </inglise>
<eesti>5) poolte vastutust; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the liability of parties; </inglise>
<eesti>6) &otilde;ppekavade ja &otilde;ppevormide koefitsiente. </eesti>
<inglise>6) the factors for the curricula and forms of study. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekoha baasmaksumuse igaks &otilde;ppeaastaks ning &otilde;ppekavade ja &otilde;ppevormide koefitsiendid kinnitab Vabariigi Valitsus. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The Government of the Republic shall approve the basic cost of a student place formed on the basis of state commissioned education for each academic year and the factors for the curricula and forms of study. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Haridusministeeriumil on kohustus finantseerida riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohta selle &otilde;ppekoha arvestusliku maksumuse ulatuses vastava &otilde;ppekavaga kehtestatud nominaalse &otilde;ppeaja l&otilde;puni. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Ministry of Education has an obligation to finance a student place formed on the basis of state commissioned education to the extent of the calculated cost of the student place until the end of the standard period of study established by the corresponding curriculum. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) &Uuml;likoolil on kohustus: </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A university has an obligation to: </inglise>
<eesti>1) luua v&otilde;imalused &otilde;ppekava t&auml;itmiseks &uuml;li&otilde;pilasele, kes &otilde;pib riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohal; </eesti>
<inglise>1) create opportunities for students who study in student places formed on the basis of state commissioned education to complete a curriculum; </inglise>
<eesti>2) informeerida Haridusministeeriumi riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohtade h&otilde;ives toimunud muudatustest. </eesti>
<inglise>2) inform the Ministry of Education of changes to the number of students in student places formed on the basis of state commissioned education. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohal &uuml;likoolis &otilde;ppiv &uuml;li&otilde;pilane v&otilde;i &uuml;likooli l&otilde;petanud isik ei saa teist korda asuda &otilde;ppima riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohale samal k&otilde;rgharidusastmel. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) A student studying at a university in a student place formed on the basis of state commissioned education or a person who has graduated from a university on the basis of state commissioned education shall not commence studies at a university for a second time at the same academic level in a student place formed on the basis of state commissioned education. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohtadel &otilde;ppivate &uuml;li&otilde;pilaste ja nende &otilde;ppekohtade h&otilde;ives tekkinud muudatuste arvestust peab Haridusministeerium." </eesti>
<inglise>(7) The Ministry of Education shall keep records of students who study in student places formed on the basis of state commissioned education and of changes in the number of students in such student places." </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Seadust t&auml;iendatakse &sect;-ga 13 (2) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>Section 13 (2) is added to the Act worded as follows: </inglise>
