<inglise>"&sect; 13 (2). </inglise>
<eesti>Riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohtade t&auml;itmine </eesti>
<inglise>Filling of student places formed on basis of state commissioned education </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohtade esmat&auml;itmine toimub &uuml;likooli n&otilde;ukogu kehtestatud korras vastavalt antud &otilde;ppekava j&auml;rgi &otilde;ppida soovijate sisseastumistulemuste paremusj&auml;rjestusele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Student places formed on the basis of state commissioned education shall initially be filled pursuant to the procedure established by the board of the university and according to the results of the entrance examinations of persons who wish to study according to the given curriculum. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel &otilde;ppinud &uuml;li&otilde;pilane arvatakse &uuml;likoolist v&auml;lja enne &otilde;ppekavaga kehtestatud nominaalse &otilde;ppeaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumist, on &uuml;likoolil &otilde;igus asendada riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohal &otilde;ppinud &uuml;li&otilde;pilane teise &uuml;li&otilde;pilasega, eelistades konkurentsi korral parima &otilde;piedukusega &uuml;li&otilde;pilast. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If a student who studies in a student place formed on the basis of state commissioned education is dismissed from a university before the end of the standard period of study established by the curriculum, the university has the right to replace the student who studied in the student place formed on the basis of state commissioned education and, in the case of competition, the student with the best academic achievement shall be preferred. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui &uuml;likool ei asenda riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohal &otilde;ppinud &uuml;li&otilde;pilast teise &uuml;li&otilde;pilasega v&otilde;i p&auml;rast &otilde;ppekavaga kehtestatud nominaalse &otilde;ppeaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumist ei ole antud &otilde;ppekava t&auml;ies mahus t&auml;itnud &uuml;li&otilde;pilaste arv v&otilde;rdne riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohtade arvuga, v&auml;hendatakse j&auml;rgmisel eelarveaastal riiklikku koolitustellimust selle &otilde;ppekoha finantseerimise v&otilde;rra. </eesti>
<inglise>If the university does not replace the student who studied in the student place formed on the basis of state commissioned education with another student or the number of students who completed a given curriculum at the end of the standard period of study established by the curriculum is not equal to the number of student places formed on the basis of state commissioned education at the end of the standard period of study established by the curriculum, state commissioned education shall be reduced to the extent of the financing of this student place in the following budgetary year. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. </inglise>
<eesti>Seadust t&auml;iendatakse &sect;-ga 13 (3) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>Section 13 (3) is added to the Act worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"13 <hi rend="sup"> 3. </hi>. </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 13 (3). </inglise>
<eesti>&Otilde;ppekulude h&uuml;vitamine </eesti>
<inglise>Reimbursement of study costs </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Uuml;likool v&otilde;ib n&otilde;uda &otilde;ppekulude h&uuml;vitamist: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A university may request reimbursement of study costs from the following: </inglise>
<eesti>1) riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel &otilde;ppinud diplomi-, bakalaureuse- v&otilde;i doktori&otilde;ppe &uuml;li&otilde;pilastelt, kes j&auml;tkavad &otilde;pinguid riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel moodustatud &otilde;ppekohal sama &otilde;ppekava j&auml;rgi p&auml;rast &otilde;ppekavaga kehtestatud nominaalse &otilde;ppeaja l&otilde;ppemist - esimese &otilde;ppeaasta eest kuni &otilde;ppekoha poole baasmaksumuseni, teise ja iga j&auml;rgneva &otilde;ppeaasta eest kuni &otilde;ppekoha kogu baasmaksumuseni; </eesti>
<inglise>1) students who studied in diploma, bachelor's or doctorate study on the basis of state commissioned education and who continue studies in the student place formed on the basis of state commissioned education according to the same curriculum after termination of the standard period of study established by the curriculum - up to a half of the basic cost of a student place for the first academic year and up to the total basic cost of a student place for the second and each subsequent academic year; </inglise>
<eesti>2) riikliku koolitustellimuse alusel &otilde;ppinud &uuml;li&otilde;pilastelt, kes l&auml;bivad bakalaureuse&otilde;ppele j&auml;rgneva &otilde;petajakoolituse koolitusprogrammi, p&auml;rast m&otilde;lema &otilde;ppekava summaarse nominaalse &otilde;ppeaja l&otilde;ppemist - esimese &otilde;ppeaasta eest kuni &otilde;ppekoha poole baasmaksumuseni, teise ja iga j&auml;rgneva &otilde;ppeaasta eest kuni &otilde;ppekoha kogu baasmaksumuseni; </eesti>
<inglise>2) students who studied on the basis of state commissioned education and who complete a teacher training programme which follows bachelor's study, after termination of the summated standard period of study of both curricula - up to a half of the basic cost of a student place for the first academic year and up to the total basic cost of a student place for the second and each subsequent academic year; </inglise>
<eesti>3) &uuml;li&otilde;pilastelt, kes &otilde;pivad v&auml;ljaspool riiklikku koolitustellimust - &uuml;likooli poolt kehtestatud korras ja tingimustel kogu &otilde;ppeaja eest. </eesti>
<inglise>3) students who study outside state commissioned education - for the whole period of study pursuant to the procedure and under the conditions established by the university. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) &Otilde;ppekulude h&uuml;vitamisest vabastatakse &uuml;li&otilde;pilane: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A student shall be released of reimbursement of study costs if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kes on I v&otilde;i II grupi invaliid; </eesti>
<inglise>1) he or she is a Category I or II disabled person; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kes on alaealise lapse v&otilde;i lapsinvaliidi vanem v&otilde;i eestkostja; </eesti>
<inglise>2) he or she is a parent or guardian of a minor or disabled child; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kui see on ette n&auml;htud teiste seadustega. </eesti>
<inglise>3) it is prescribed by other Acts. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 8. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 8. </inglise>
