<inglise>1) basis training with a standard duration of six years; </inglise>
<eesti>2) residentuurist nominaalkestusega kaks kuni viis aastat. </eesti>
<inglise>2) residency with a standard duration of two to five years. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Arsti&otilde;ppe residentuuri l&auml;bimine toimub Sotsiaalministeeriumi m&auml;&auml;ratud tervishoiuasutuses ja Sotsiaalministeeriumi finantseerimisel. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Medical training residency shall be completed in the health care institutions determined by the Ministry of Social Affairs and shall be financed by the Ministry of Social Affairs. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Arsti&otilde;ppe residendid on v&otilde;rdsustatud doktorantidega. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The residents of medical training are deemed to be equal to doctorate candidates. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Arsti p&otilde;hi&otilde;ppe, loomaarstiteaduse, proviisori, hambaarstiteaduse ja arhitekt-inseneri &otilde;ppekava l&auml;bimine annab &otilde;iguse j&auml;tkata samal erialal &otilde;pinguid doktori&otilde;ppes." </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The completion of a curriculum of medical science, veterinary medicine, pharmacy, dentistry or architecture-engineering grants the right to continue studies in the same field in doctorate study." </inglise>
