<eesti>&Uuml;likoolide, &uuml;li&otilde;pilasomavalitsuste ja &uuml;li&otilde;pilaskondade p&otilde;hikirjad viiakse k&auml;esoleva seadusega vastavusse kuue kuu jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>The statutes of universities, student self-governments and Student Bodies shall be brought into compliance with this Act within six months after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;likoolides, mille juures tegutsevad nii &uuml;li&otilde;pilasomavalitsus kui ka &uuml;li&otilde;pilaskond, v&otilde;tab &uuml;htse &uuml;li&otilde;pilaskonna p&otilde;hikirja vastu seaduse j&otilde;ustumise hetkeks k&otilde;ige hiljem valitud esinduskogu, mille valimistel v&otilde;isid osaleda k&otilde;ik &uuml;likooli &uuml;li&otilde;pilased. </eesti>
<inglise>In universities where both a student self-government and a Student Body operate, the representative body which was elected last before the time of entry into force of this Act and which could be elected by all students of the university shall adopt the uniform statutes of the Student Body. </inglise>
